flowchart LR
    Client([Client])
    Bucket[Bucket Service<br/>ACL, policies]
    Meta[Metadata Service<br/>bucket,key to<br/>piece locations]
    MetaStore[("Metadata Store<br/>sharded, replicated")]
    Data[Data Nodes<br/>erasure-coded 6+3<br/>across racks/AZs]
    Pieces[("Piece Storage<br/>D1 D2 D3 ... P1 P2 P3")]
    BG[Background Jobs<br/>GC, Repair, Scrub]

    Client -->|PUT/GET auth| Bucket
    Client -->|lookup / write meta| Meta
    Meta --> MetaStore
    Client -->|stream pieces| Data
    Data --> Pieces
    BG -.->|repair / scrub| Pieces
    BG -.->|update locations| MetaStore

